    <link href="https://zycinhk.github.io/2019/08/13/NEXT%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/"/>
    <id>https://zycinhk.github.io/2019/08/13/NEXT主题美化（一）/</id>
    <published>2019-08-13T09:10:36.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-08-13T09:41:25.656Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p> 最近看到很多大牛都在自己的博客下方加了一个动态的心形，之前将主题配置文件中改成heart，footer.yml下添加</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;span <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span>="<span class="title">with</span>-<span class="title">love</span>" <span class="title">id</span>="<span class="title">animate</span>"&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"> &lt;i class="fa fa-&#123;&#123; theme.footer.icon.name &#125;&#125;"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>页脚的图标，会变成一颗静态的黑色❤；</p><p>查看很多国内外Blog，给出的方法都是，将主题配置下的icon如下配置</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">icon:</span><br><span class="line">name: heart</span><br><span class="line">animated: true //用来设置为动态</span><br><span class="line">color: <span class="string">"#ff0000"</span> //hex表示，<span class="comment">#ff0000为red</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是多次尝试修改未果，通过查看成型blog中的source code也无法查看到配置；</p><hr><p>在多次尝试和搜索，得到如下方法：</p><p><font color="green" size="5" font face="黑体">让页脚的小心心跳动起来</font></p><p>首先修改主题配置文件：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">copy文件位置：~/hexo/themes/next/_config.yml</span><br><span class="line">copyfooter:      icon: user修改成heart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后修改<code>footer.swig</code>：</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">copy文件位置：~/hexo/themes/next/layout/_partials/footer.swig</span><br><span class="line">copy&lt;span class="with-love"&gt;修改成&lt;span class="with-love" id="heart"&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着编辑<code>custom.styl</code>：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">copy文件位置：~/hexo/themes/next/source/css/_custom/custom.styl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在其中加入</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 自定义页脚跳动的心样式</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@keyframes heartAnimate &#123;    </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="number">0</span>%,<span class="number">100</span>%&#123;transform:scale(<span class="number">1</span>);&#125;    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="number">10</span>%,<span class="number">30</span>%&#123;transform:scale(<span class="number">0.9</span>);&#125;    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="number">20</span>%,<span class="number">40</span>%,<span class="number">60</span>%,<span class="number">80</span>%&#123;transform:scale(<span class="number">1.1</span>);&#125;    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="number">50</span>%,<span class="number">70</span>%&#123;transform:scale(<span class="number">1.1</span>);&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#heart &#123;    </span></span><br><span class="line">    animation: heartAnimate <span class="number">1.33</span>s ease-<span class="keyword">in</span>-out infinite;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">.<span class="keyword">with</span>-love &#123;   </span><br><span class="line">    color: rgb(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
