    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="背景：换了一台电脑下拉源码之后，hexo-d-报错-【fatal-in-unpopulated-submodule-‘-deploy-git’】"><a href="#背景：换了一台电脑下拉源码之后，hexo-d-报错-【fatal-in-unpopulated-submodule-‘-deploy-git’】" class="headerlink" title="背景：换了一台电脑下拉源码之后，hexo d 报错 【fatal: in unpopulated submodule ‘.deploy_git’】"></a>背景：换了一台电脑下拉源码之后，hexo d 报错 【fatal: in unpopulated submodule ‘.deploy_git’】</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fatal: <span class="keyword">in</span> unpopulated submodule <span class="string">'.deploy_git'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">FATAL Something<span class="string">'s wrong. Maybe you can find the solution here: http://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Error: Spawn failed</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at ChildProcess.&lt;anonymous&gt; 。。。。。。】</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>目前找到的解决方案是，删除blog下的，.deploy_git文件夹，然后重新clean，hexo g， 然后再hexo d就可以了；</p><p>或者</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ rm -rf .deploy_git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>** 网上也有人说安装相关依赖也能解决：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git –save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
